@startuml
' Forzamos una disposición compacta y plana
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 10
skinparam ranksep 20

rectangle "Healthcare Provider" as HP {
  component "Treating Physician" as Doc
}

rectangle "Public Health" as PH {
  component "FOPH Reporting System" as FOPH
}

' --- Relations ---
' Usamos flecha simple para que PlantUML gestione el espacio óptimamente
Doc -> FOPH : Transmits Clinical Report

@enduml